Comment.val: /*Function to retrieve the security mutation information per account.*/

Text.val: AccountId or AccountNumber must be present:
The instrument of the given Instrument attributes can't be derived:
First account found with same accountnumber:
Ordered by TransDate DESC Transnumber DESC
- If an instrumentId is present in the request only return 1 instrument
- If no instrumentId is present in the request,return all securites plus all options
- If no symbol is present in the request, return all securities plus all options (No further selection is possible!)
- If symbol is present, return all securties plus all options ( further selection is executed!)
- If optiontype is present but empty, don't return options but only the security
Pagesize + 1 to be able to detect if a next page is present in the current query.

SQL_STMT_U.val: select FULL_QUERY.*,rownum "ROW_NUM" from ( select pom.pom_peildatum "TRANS_DATE", pom.pom_transactienr "TRANS_NUMBER", pom.pom_mutatie_aantal "POM_MUTATIE_AANTAL", pom.pom_mutatie_prijscl "POM_MUTATIE_PRIJSCL", pom.pom_mutatie_prijsbe "POM_MUTATIE_PRIJSBE", pom.pom_saldo_positie "POM_SALDO_POSITIE", (pom.pom_peildatum||';'||to_char(pom.pom_transactienr,'fm099999999'))"SORT_DATE_TRANSNR", be.be_volgnummer "BE_VOLGNUMMER", be.be_oms_1 "BE_OMS1", be.be_muntsoort "BE_MUNTSOORT", be.be_prijs_factor "BE_PRIJS_FACTOR", be.be_aantal_cijfers_display "BE_AANTAL_CIJFERS_DISPLAY", tr.tr_volgnummer "TR_VOLGNUMMER", tr.tr_indicatie "TR_INDICATIE", tr.tr_boekdatum "TR_BOEKDATUM", m.code "MC_MUTATIECODE", m.external_code "MC_EXTERNAL_CODE", m.description "MC_DESCRIPTION" from posmuttransdatum pom inner join beleggingsinstrument be on be.be_volgnummer=pom.pom_be_volgnummer inner join transactions tr on tr.tr_volgnummer=pom.pom_tr_volgnummer left outer join mutationcodes m on m.code = tr.tr_mutatiecode where :1 order by pom_peildatum DESC, pom_transactienr DESC ) FULL_QUERY where :2
